{"tid":2051985,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【六四事件31周年】美國白宮聲明：中國應履行對香港承諾 停止迫害少數族裔及宗教人士","createTime":"2020-06-05T07:33:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T07:35:33.000Z","uid":70063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7bcd48327c485b97cfea1d6ffd1bf19a9ad36b42","tid":2051985,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:33:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau/status/1268754468415438848?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAinHKMacau%2Fstatus%2F1268754468415438848%3Fs%3D19&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EluZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=0bc6ba2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSAinHKMacau%2Fstatus%2F1268754468415438848%3Fs%3D19&h=c6800782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/USAinHKMacau/status/1268754468415438848?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮在六四事件31周年發表聲明，促請中國尊重人權、履行對香港承諾、及停止迫害少數族裔及宗教人士。<br />\n<br />\n聲明說：「美國人支持所有中國人民追求基本權利，包括問責及代議政制權利以及言論、集會和宗教信仰自由。」白宮聲明直指1989年天安門事件「屠殺」示威者慘案不會被忘記，促請北京準確交代死傷數字。<br />\n<br />\n總統特朗普的新聞秘書麥肯阿尼（Kayleigh McEnany）在聲明說：「中國共產黨屠殺手無寸鐵的中國平民，是永不會被遺忘的悲劇。美國呼籲中國紀念所有犧牲了性命的人，全面交代1989年6月4日在天安門周圍發生的事件中被殺、拘禁或失蹤人士的資料。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200605/ROFESHKDBJVCMCKHGCXBJYLFDA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200605%2FROFESHKDBJVCMCKHGCXBJYLFDA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=OUx24mKaoEPTVTG9WcU5EluZLtDw6XEhdFI90r4xbX0%3D&h=c3b84560\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200605%2FROFESHKDBJVCMCKHGCXBJYLFDA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=db9ea8d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200605/ROFESHKDBJVCMCKHGCXBJYLFDA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"67d32a8baa4dac9f8fc516649e5cba57a80a3637","tid":2051985,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T07:35:33.000Z","msg":"無侵侵無美國<br />\n我地比坦克碌過應該都無人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}